---
// Hero.astro
// Propósito: Sección principal de impacto visual.
---

<section class="hero">
	<div class="hero-container">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<span class="badge">Nuevas Aventuras 2024</span>
			<h1>Viste su <span>imaginación</span> con suavidad</h1>
			<p>Ropa diseñada para jugar, crecer y soñar. Algodón orgánico y colores que acompañan cada paso.</p>
			<div class="hero-actions">
				<a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Ver Colección</a>
				<a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Niños & Niñas</a>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="hero-visual">
			<div class="blob-container">
				<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519704943920-1844582b75bc?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800" alt="Niños jugando" class="hero-img" />
			</div>
			<!-- Elementos decorativos (Firma) -->
			<div class="bubble bubble-1"></div>
			<div class="bubble bubble-2"></div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.hero {
		min-height: 100vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding-top: 100px;
		padding-bottom: 60px;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.hero-container {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: calc(var(--space) * 8);
		align-items: center;
		padding: 0 calc(var(--space) * 4);
	}

	.hero-content {
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.badge {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: calc(var(--space) * 0.75) calc(var(--space) * 2);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
		border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--brand-pink);
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--space) * 3);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
		line-height: 1.1;
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--space) * 3);
	}

	h1 span {
		color: var(--white);
		text-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
	}

	p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
		margin-bottom: calc(var(--space) * 5);
		max-width: 500px;
	}

	.hero-actions {
		display: flex;
		gap: calc(var(--space) * 2);
	}

	.btn {
		padding: calc(var(--space) * 2) calc(var(--space) * 4);
		border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
		font-weight: 700;
		transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
		display: inline-block;
	}

	.btn:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-float);
	}

	.btn-primary {
		background: var(--brand-pink);
		color: var(--white);
	}

	.btn-secondary {
		background: var(--white);
		color: var(--brand-blue);
		border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
	}

	/* Firma: Blob y Burbujas */
	.hero-visual {
		position: relative;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
	}

	.blob-container {
		width: 100%;
		aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
		border-radius: var(--radius-blob);
		overflow: hidden;
		animation: morph 10s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-subtle);
	}

	.hero-img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		transition: transform 0.5s ease;
	}

	.blob-container:hover .hero-img {
		transform: scale(1.05);
	}

	.bubble {
		position: absolute;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
		backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
		z-index: 1;
		animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	.bubble-1 {
		width: 80px;
		height: 80px;
		top: -20px;
		right: 20px;
		background: var(--brand-blue);
		opacity: 0.4;
	}

	.bubble-2 {
		width: 120px;
		height: 120px;
		bottom: -30px;
		left: -20px;
		background: var(--brand-pink);
		opacity: 0.4;
		animation-delay: -3s;
	}

	@keyframes morph {
		0% { border-radius: 40% 60% 70% 30% / 40% 50% 60% 50%; }
		100% { border-radius: 60% 40% 30% 70% / 60% 30% 70% 40%; }
	}

	@keyframes float {
		0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
		50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
	}

	@media (max-width: 968px) {
		.hero-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			text-align: center;
			gap: calc(var(--space) * 6);
		}
		
		.hero-content {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
		}

		.hero-visual {
			max-width: 400px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}
	}
</style>
